{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775877184461,"sessionID":"ses_28578efe2ffeHdJlje1Uvxen4e","part":{"id":"prt_d7a875b97001qUY6XEO7hsEHu9","messageID":"msg_d7a873990001yjlgYS9SoL04Aq","sessionID":"ses_28578efe2ffeHdJlje1Uvxen4e","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-57345d7ce45a443c94ec5d2454377458","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Specification — MetadataService 与数据模型\n2: \n3: AR: AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型\n4: Module: cmd/cli\n5: Language: Python\n6: Size: M\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Requirement: MetadataService 初始化\n11: \n12: The system SHALL provide `MetadataService` as a service class for metadata file operations.\n13: \n14: ### Scenario: 默认构造\n15: \n16: - **GIVEN** `MetadataService` is instantiated\n17: - **WHEN** no arguments are provided\n18: - **THEN** `verbose` SHALL default to `False`\n19: \n20: ### Scenario: verbose 参数传入\n21: \n22: - **GIVEN** `MetadataService(verbose=True)` is instantiated\n23: - **WHEN** the instance is created\n24: - **THEN** `self.verbose` SHALL be `True`\n25: \n26: ---\n27: \n28: ## Requirement: AgentMetadata 数据模型 (Pydantic BaseModel)\n29: \n30: The system SHALL define `AgentMetadata` as a Pydantic `BaseModel` with field validators for language, build_mode, and port.\n31: \n32: ### Scenario: 必填字段验证\n33: \n34: - **GIVEN** `AgentMetadata` is instantiated\n35: - **WHEN** `agent_name` or `entrypoint` is not provided\n36: - **THEN** Pydantic SHALL raise `ValidationError` (fields marked with `Field(..., description=...)` are required)\n37: \n38: ### Scenario: 可选字段默认值\n39: \n40: - **GIVEN** `AgentMetadata` is instantiated without optional fields\n41: - **WHEN** defaults are applied\n42: - **THEN** the following defaults SHALL be used:\n43:   - `description`: `\"\"`\n44:   - `language`: `\"python\"`\n45:   - `port`: `8080`\n46:   - `build_mode`: `\"local\"`\n47:   - `region`: `\"\"`\n48:   - `version`: `\"\"`\n49:   - `image`: `default_factory=dict` (empty dict)\n50:   - `auth`: `default_factory=dict` (empty dict)\n51:   - `requirements_file`: `\"requirements.txt\"`\n52:   - `registry_url`: `\"\"`\n53:   - `registry_username`: `\"\"`\n54:   - `registry_password`: `\"\"`\n55:   - `agent_endpoint`: `\"\"`\n56:   - `workload_manager_url`: `\"\"`\n57:   - `router_url`: `\"\"`\n58:   - `readiness_probe_path`: `\"\"`\n59:   - `readiness_probe_port`: `8080`\n60:   - `agent_id`: `\"\"`\n61:   - `session_id`: `\"\"`\n62:   - `k8s_deployment`: `default_factory=dict` (empty dict)\n63: \n64: ### Scenario: language 字段验证 — 大写转换\n65: \n66: - **GIVEN** `AgentMetadata` receives `language=\"Python\"` or `\"PYTHON\"`\n67: - **WHEN** the field validator runs\n68: - **THEN** the value SHALL be lowercased to `\"python\"` and accepted\n69: \n70: ### Scenario: language 字段验证 — 非允许值拒绝\n71: \n72: - **GIVEN** `AgentMetadata` receives `language=\"go\"` or `\"ruby\"`\n73: - **WHEN** the field validator runs\n74: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise `ValueError(\"language must be one of ['python', 'java']\")`\n75: \n76: ### Scenario: build_mode 字段验证 — 大写转换\n77: \n78: - **GIVEN** `AgentMetadata` receives `build_mode=\"Local\"` or `\"LOCAL\"`\n79: - **WHEN** the field validator runs\n80: - **THEN** the value SHALL be lowercased to `\"local\"` and accepted\n81: \n82: ### Scenario: build_mode 字段验证 — 非允许值拒绝\n83: \n84: - **GIVEN** `AgentMetadata` receives `build_mode=\"docker\"` or `\"remote\"`\n85: - **WHEN** the field validator runs\n86: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise `ValueError(\"build_mode must be one of ['local', 'cloud']\")`\n87: \n88: ### Scenario: port 字段验证 — 有效范围\n89: \n90: - **GIVEN** `AgentMetadata` receives `port=8080` or `port=1` or `port=65535`\n91: - **WHEN** the field validator runs\n92: - **THEN** the value SHALL be accepted\n93: \n94: ### Scenario: port 字段验证 — 超出范围拒绝\n95: \n96: - **GIVEN** `AgentMetadata` receives `port=0` or `port=65536` or `port=-1`\n97: - **WHEN** the field validator runs\n98: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise `ValueError(\"port must be between 1 and 65535\")`\n99: \n100: ---\n101: \n102: ## Requirement: MetadataService.load_metadata\n103: \n104: The system SHALL load metadata from YAML files with primary filename `agent_metadata.yaml` and fallback order: `agent.yaml`, `metadata.yaml`.\n105: \n106: ### Scenario: 主文件存在\n107: \n108: - **GIVEN** `{workspace_path}/agent_metadata.yaml` exists\n109: - **WHEN** `load_metadata(workspace_path)` is called\n110: - **THEN** the system SHALL:\n111:   - Read the file content with `yaml.safe_load`\n112:   - Construct `AgentMetadata(**data)` from parsed YAML\n113:   - Return the `AgentMetadata` instance\n114: \n115: ### Scenario: 主文件不存在 — 回退到 agent.yaml\n116: \n117: - **GIVEN** `agent_metadata.yaml` does NOT exist but `agent.yaml` exists\n118: - **WHEN** `load_metadata(workspace_path)` is called\n119: - **THEN** the system SHALL load from `agent.yaml` and return `AgentMetadata`\n120: \n121: ### Scenario: 主和次级文件不存在 — 回退到 metadata.yaml\n122: \n123: - **GIVEN** `agent_metadata.yaml` and `agent.yaml` do NOT exist but `metadata.yaml` exists\n124: - **WHEN** `load_metadata(workspace_path)` is called\n125: - **THEN** the system SHALL load from `metadata.yaml` and return `AgentMetadata`\n126: \n127: ### Scenario: 所有元数据文件不存在\n128: \n129: - **GIVEN** none of `agent_metadata.yaml`, `agent.yaml`, `metadata.yaml` exist in workspace\n130: - **WHEN** `load_metadata(workspace_path)` is called\n131: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise `FileNotFoundError(\"No metadata file found in workspace: {workspace_path}\")`\n132: \n133: ### Scenario: YAML 内容为空或 null\n134: \n135: - **GIVEN** the metadata file exists but content is empty or YAML parses to `None`\n136: - **WHEN** the file is loaded\n137: - **THEN** the system SHALL treat empty content as `{}` and create `AgentMetadata` with defaults\n138: \n139: ### Scenario: YAML 内容字段类型错误\n140: \n141: - **GIVEN** metadata YAML contains `port: \"not-a-number\"` (invalid type)\n142: - **WHEN** `AgentMetadata(**data)` validation runs\n143: - **THEN** Pydantic SHALL raise `ValidationError` for the type mismatch\n144: \n145: ---\n146: \n147: ## Requirement: MetadataService.save_metadata\n148: \n149: The system SHALL persist metadata to `{workspace_path}/agent_metadata.yaml` using `yaml.dump` with specific formatting options.\n150: \n151: ### Scenario: 保存到主文件路径\n152: \n153: - **GIVEN** `workspace_path` exists and `metadata` is an `AgentMetadata` instance\n154: - **WHEN** `save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)` is called\n155: - **THEN** the system SHALL:\n156:   - Write to `{workspace_path}/agent_metadata.yaml`\n157:   - Return the file `Path` object\n158: \n159: ### Scenario: YAML 输出格式参数\n160: \n161: - **GIVEN** metadata is being saved\n162: - **WHEN** `yaml.dump` is called\n163: - **THEN** the following parameters SHALL be used:\n164:   - `default_flow_style=False` (block format, not inline)\n165:   - `indent=2`\n166:   - `sort_keys=False` (preserve field order)\n167:   - Data from `metadata.model_dump(exclude_none=True)` (exclude `None` fields)\n168: \n169: ### Scenario: 空字典字段包含在输出\n170: \n171: - **GIVEN** `image`, `auth`, or `k8s_deployment` fields are empty dicts `{}` (not `None`)\n172: - **WHEN** metadata is saved\n173: - **THEN** empty dicts SHALL be included in YAML output (because `exclude_none=True` only excludes `None`, not empty dicts)\n174: \n175: ### Scenario: None 值字段排除\n176: \n177: - **GIVEN** a field value is `None` (not an empty string or empty dict)\n178: - **WHEN** metadata is saved with `exclude_none=True`\n179: - **THEN** that field SHALL NOT appear in the YAML output\n180: \n181: ---\n182: \n183: ## Requirement: MetadataService.update_metadata (待实现)\n184: \n185: The system SHALL provide `update_metadata` to load existing metadata, apply updates, and save.\n186: \n187: ### Scenario: 更新部分字段\n188: \n189: - **GIVEN** workspace has existing metadata file with `version=\"\"` and `description=\"old\"`\n190: - **WHEN** `update_metadata(workspace_path, {\"version\": \"v1.0.0\", \"description\": \"new desc\"})` is called\n191: - **THEN** the system SHALL:\n192:   - Load existing metadata via `load_metadata`\n193:   - Apply the updates dict to metadata fields\n194:   - Save via `save_metadata`\n195:   - Return the updated `AgentMetadata` instance\n196: \n197: ### Scenario: 更新触发验证错误\n198: \n199: - **GIVEN** updates dict contains `{\"language\": \"rust\"}`\n200: - **WHEN** the updated metadata is validated\n201: - **THEN** `AgentMetadata` validator SHALL raise `ValueError` for invalid language\n202: \n203: ---\n204: \n205: ## Requirement: MetadataService.validate_workspace (待实现)\n206: \n207: The system SHALL validate workspace structure based on the language specified in metadata.\n208: \n209: ### Scenario: workspace 路径不存在\n210: \n211: - **GIVEN** `workspace_path` does NOT exist or is NOT a directory\n212: - **WHEN** `validate_workspace(workspace_path)` is called\n213: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise `ValueError` with message indicating path does not exist or is not a directory\n214: \n215: ### Scenario: Python workspace 验证成功\n216: \n217: - **GIVEN** metadata `language == \"python\"` and workspace contains at least one `.py` file\n218: - **WHEN** `_validate_python_workspace(workspace_path, metadata)` runs\n219: - **THEN** the system SHALL return without raising an error\n220: \n221: ### Scenario: Python workspace 无 Python 文件\n222: \n223: - **GIVEN** metadata `language == \"python\"` and workspace has NO `.py` files\n224: - **WHEN** `_validate_python_workspace(workspace_path, metadata)` runs\n225: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise `ValueError(\"No Python files found in workspace\")`\n226: \n227: ### Scenario: Java workspace 验证成功\n228: \n229: - **GIVEN** metadata `language == \"java\"` and workspace contains `pom.xml`\n230: - **WHEN** `_validate_java_workspace(workspace_path, metadata)` runs\n231: - **THEN** the system SHALL return without raising an error\n232: \n233: ### Scenario: Java workspace 无 pom.xml\n234: \n235: - **GIVEN** metadata `language == \"java\"` and workspace has NO `pom.xml`\n236: - **WHEN** `_validate_java_workspace(workspace_path, metadata)` runs\n237: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise `ValueError(\"pom.xml not found in workspace\")`\n238: \n239: ---\n240: \n241: ## Requirement: MetadataOptions 数据类 (pack_models.py)\n242: \n243: The system SHALL define `MetadataOptions` as a dataclass for CLI option mapping.\n244: \n245: ### Scenario: 默认值设置\n246: \n247: - **GIVEN** `MetadataOptions` is instantiated without arguments\n248: - **WHEN** defaults are applied\n249: - **THEN** the following defaults SHALL be used:\n250:   - `agent_name`: `None`\n251:   - `language`: `\"python\"`\n252:   - `entrypoint`: `None`\n253:   - `port`: `8080`\n254:   - `build_mode`: `\"local\"`\n255:   - `requirements_file`: `None`\n256:   - `description`: `None`\n257:   - `workload_manager_url`: `\"\"`\n258:   - `router_url`: `\"\"`\n259:   - `readiness_probe_path`: `\"\"`\n260:   - `readiness_probe_port`: `8080`\n261:   - `registry_url`: `\"\"`\n262:   - `registry_username`: `\"\"`\n263:   - `registry_password`: `\"\"`\n264:   - `agent_endpoint`: `\"\"`\n265: \n266: ### Scenario: from_options 工厂方法 — 正常输入\n267: \n268: - **GIVEN** `options = {\"agent_name\": \"my-agent\", \"language\": \"java\", \"port\": 9090}`\n269: - **WHEN** `MetadataOptions.from_options(options)` is called\n270: - **THEN** the system SHALL:\n271:   - Filter out entries where value is `None`\n272:   - Create `MetadataOptions` instance with remaining values\n273:   - Return instance with `agent_name=\"my-agent\"`, `language=\"java\"`, `port=9090`\n274: \n275: ### Scenario: from_options 工厂方法 — 过滤 None 值\n276: \n277: - **GIVEN** `options = {\"agent_name\": None, \"language\": \"python\", \"entrypoint\": None}`\n278: - **WHEN** `MetadataOptions.from_options(options)` is called\n279: - **THEN** the system SHALL:\n280:   - Filter out `\"agent_name\"` and `\"entrypoint\"` because their values are `None`\n281:   - Return instance using defaults for filtered fields\n282: \n283: ### Scenario: from_options 工厂方法 — 未知键忽略\n284: \n285: - **GIVEN** `options = {\"agent_name\": \"test\", \"unknown_field\": \"value\"}`\n286: - **WHEN** `MetadataOptions.from_options(options)` is called\n287: - **THEN** the system SHALL:\n288:   - Pass only matching dataclass fields to constructor\n289:   - Ignore `unknown_field` or raise error depending on implementation\n290: \n291: ---\n292: \n293: ## Requirement: Metadata 文件格式规范\n294: \n295: The system SHALL use YAML format with specific naming and formatting conventions.\n296: \n297: ### Scenario: 主文件名 agent_metadata.yaml\n298: \n299: - **GIVEN** metadata is saved\n300: - **WHEN** `MetadataService.save_metadata` runs\n301: - **THEN** the primary filename SHALL be `agent_metadata.yaml` (not `agentcube.yaml`)\n302: \n303: ### Scenario: 加载文件名优先级\n304: \n305: - **GIVEN** multiple metadata files may exist\n306: - **WHEN** `MetadataService.load_metadata` searches for files\n307: - **THEN** the priority order SHALL be:\n308:   1. `agent_metadata.yaml` (primary)\n309:   2. `agent.yaml` (fallback)\n310:   3. `metadata.yaml` (secondary fallback)\n311: \n312: ---\n313: \n314: ## Requirement: Pydantic validator 使用 field_validator\n315: \n316: The system SHALL use Pydantic v2 `field_validator` decorator for field validation.\n317: \n318: ### Scenario: validator 方法签名\n319: \n320: - **GIVEN** a field validator is defined\n321: - **WHEN** using `@field_validator(\"language\")`\n322: - **THEN** the validator method SHALL be a `@classmethod` and receive `v: str` (the field value)\n323: \n324: ### Scenario: validator 返回转换值\n325: \n326: - **GIVEN** `language` validator lowercases the input\n327: - **WHEN** input is `\"Python\"`\n328: - **THEN** validator SHALL return `\"python\"` (the transformed value)\n329: \n330: ---\n331: \n332: ## Implementation Files\n333: \n334: | File | Purpose |\n335: |------|---------|\n336: | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | `AgentMetadata` model, `MetadataService` class |\n337: | `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | `MetadataOptions` dataclass |\n338: \n339: ---\n340: \n341: ## Dependencies\n342: \n343: | Package | Purpose |\n344: |---------|---------|\n345: | `pydantic>=2.0.0` | `BaseModel`, `Field`, `field_validator` |\n346: | `pyyaml>=6.0` | `yaml.safe_load`, `yaml.dump` |\n347: | `pathlib` | `Path` for file operations |\n348: \n349: ---\n350: \n351: ## Validation Checklist\n352: \n353: - [ ] `AgentMetadata` defined as Pydantic `BaseModel`\n354: - [ ] Required fields: `agent_name`, `entrypoint` (use `Field(...)`)\n355: - [ ] Optional fields have correct defaults (`\"\"`, `default_factory=dict`, etc.)\n356: - [ ] `validate_language` accepts `python`/`java`, lowercases input, rejects others\n357: - [ ] `validate_build_mode` accepts `local`/`cloud`, lowercases input, rejects others\n358: - [ ] `validate_port` accepts `1..65535`, rejects out-of-range\n359: - [ ] `MetadataService.__init__` accepts `verbose` parameter\n360: - [ ] `load_metadata` checks `agent_metadata.yaml` first, then `agent.yaml`, then `metadata.yaml`\n361: - [ ] `load_metadata` raises `FileNotFoundError` when no file found\n362: - [ ] `load_metadata` handles empty YAML as `{}` with defaults\n363: - [ ] `save_metadata` writes to `agent_metadata.yaml`\n364: - [ ] `save_metadata` uses `yaml.dump(default_flow_style=False, indent=2, sort_keys=False)`\n365: - [ ] `save_metadata` uses `model_dump(exclude_none=True)`\n366: - [ ] `save_metadata` returns `Path` to saved file\n367: - [ ] `MetadataOptions` dataclass with correct fields and defaults\n368: - [ ] `MetadataOptions.from_options` filters `None` values from input dict\n\n(End of file - total 368 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Specification — MetadataService 与数据模型\n\nAR: AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型\nModule: cmd/cli\nLanguage: Python\nSize: M\n\n---\n\n## Requirement: MetadataService 初始化\n\nThe system SHALL provide `MetadataService` as a service class for metadata file operations.\n\n### Scenario: 默认构造\n\n- **GIVEN** `MetadataService` is instantiated\n- **WHEN** no arguments are provided\n- **THEN** `verbose` SHALL default to `False`\n\n### Scenario: verbose 参数传入","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775877184442,"end":1775877184459}}}}
