{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775877184468,"sessionID":"ses_28578efe2ffeHdJlje1Uvxen4e","part":{"id":"prt_d7a875806001xmacm5zdkZpbpO","messageID":"msg_d7a873990001yjlgYS9SoL04Aq","sessionID":"ses_28578efe2ffeHdJlje1Uvxen4e","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-7373f66a4bd549698f6cadd5188a55ec","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-025/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-025/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型 Tasks\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型 |\n8: | Module | `cmd/cli` |\n9: | Language | Python |\n10: | Size | M |\n11: | Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n12: \n13: ---\n14: \n15: ## Task Checklist\n16: \n17: ### Phase 1: AgentMetadata Model (ST-1)\n18: \n19: - [x] **T1.1**: Implement `AgentMetadata` Pydantic BaseModel with all required fields\n20:   - Purpose: Define primary data model for agent configuration stored as YAML\n21:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py:8-30`\n22:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_valid -v`\n23: \n24: - [x] **T1.2**: Implement `language` field validator\n25:   - Purpose: Validate language is one of ['python', 'java'] with lowercase normalization\n26:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py:32-39`\n27:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_invalid_language -v`\n28: \n29: - [x] **T1.3**: Implement `build_mode` field validator\n30:   - Purpose: Validate build_mode is one of ['local', 'cloud'] with lowercase normalization\n31:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py:41-48`\n32:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_invalid_build_mode -v`\n33: \n34: - [x] **T1.4**: Implement `port` field validator\n35:   - Purpose: Validate port is in range 1-65535\n36:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py:50-55`\n37:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_invalid_port_low -v`\n38: \n39: ### Phase 2: MetadataOptions Dataclass (ST-2)\n40: \n41: - [x] **T2.1**: Implement `MetadataOptions` dataclass with all CLI options fields\n42:   - Purpose: Define dataclass for mapping command-line arguments to metadata fields\n43:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/models/pack_models.py:6-21`\n44:   - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.models.pack_models import MetadataOptions; print(MetadataOptions.__dataclass_fields__)\"`\n45: \n46: - [x] **T2.2**: Implement `MetadataOptions.from_options()` factory method\n47:   - Purpose: Create MetadataOptions from dict filtering None values\n48:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/models/pack_models.py:23-26`\n49:   - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.models.pack_models import MetadataOptions; opt = MetadataOptions.from_options({'agent_name': 'test', 'port': 8080}); print(opt.agent_name)\"`\n50: \n51: ### Phase 3: MetadataService Core Methods (ST-3)\n52: \n53: - [x] **T3.1**: Implement `MetadataService.__init__` with verbose flag\n54:   - Purpose: Initialize service with verbose flag for logging control\n55:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py:59-60`\n56:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_load_agent_metadata_yaml -v`\n57: \n58: - [x] **T3.2**: Implement `load_metadata()` with fallback filename list\n59:   - Purpose: Load metadata from workspace, falling back through ['agent_metadata.yaml', 'agent.yaml', 'metadata.yaml']\n60:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py:62-72`\n61:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_load_fallback_agent_yaml -v`\n62: \n63: - [x] **T3.3**: Implement `save_metadata()` with YAML serialization settings\n64:   - Purpose: Save metadata to agent_metadata.yaml with exclude_none, indent=2, no flow style\n65:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py:74-79`\n66:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_save_excludes_none -v`\n67: \n68: - [ ] **T3.4**: Implement `update_metadata()` method\n69:   - Purpose: Load, apply updates dict, save, and return new AgentMetadata\n70:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n71:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_update -v`\n72: \n73: - [ ] **T3.5**: Implement `validate_workspace()` method\n74:   - Purpose: Validate workspace structure and language-specific requirements\n75:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n76:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_validate_workspace_python -v`\n77: \n78: - [ ] **T3.6**: Implement `_validate_python_workspace()` helper\n79:   - Purpose: Check for at least one *.py file in workspace root\n80:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n81:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_validate_python_workspace_has_py -v`\n82: \n83: - [ ] **T3.7**: Implement `_validate_java_workspace()` helper\n84:   - Purpose: Check for pom.xml in workspace\n85:   - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n86:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_validate_java_workspace_has_pom -v`\n87: \n88: ### Phase 4: Comprehensive Unit Tests (ST-4)\n89: \n90: - [x] **T4.1**: Test AgentMetadata valid creation\n91:   - Purpose: Verify AgentMetadata creates with required fields and defaults\n92:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:11-20`\n93:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_valid -v`\n94: \n95: - [x] **T4.2**: Test AgentMetadata invalid language rejection\n96:   - Purpose: Verify ValidationError for unsupported language\n97:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:22-28`\n98:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_invalid_language -v`\n99: \n100: - [x] **T4.3**: Test AgentMetadata invalid build_mode rejection\n101:   - Purpose: Verify ValidationError for unsupported build_mode\n102:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:30-37`\n103:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_invalid_build_mode -v`\n104: \n105: - [x] **T4.4**: Test AgentMetadata port range validation\n106:   - Purpose: Verify ValidationError for port outside 1-65535 range\n107:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:39-72`\n108:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_invalid_port_high -v`\n109: \n110: - [x] **T4.5**: Test load_metadata from agent_metadata.yaml (primary)\n111:   - Purpose: Verify loading from primary filename\n112:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:76-91`\n113:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_load_agent_metadata_yaml -v`\n114: \n115: - [x] **T4.6**: Test load_metadata fallback to agent.yaml\n116:   - Purpose: Verify fallback to second filename when primary missing\n117:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:93-104`\n118:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_load_fallback_agent_yaml -v`\n119: \n120: - [x] **T4.7**: Test load_metadata fallback to metadata.yaml\n121:   - Purpose: Verify fallback to third filename when first two missing\n122:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:106-118`\n123:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_load_fallback_metadata_yaml -v`\n124: \n125: - [x] **T4.8**: Test load_metadata FileNotFoundError when all missing\n126:   - Purpose: Verify FileNotFoundError raised when no metadata files exist\n127:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:158-160`\n128:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_load_no_files -v`\n129: \n130: - [x] **T4.9**: Test save_metadata YAML format\n131:   - Purpose: Verify YAML dumped with default_flow_style=False, indent=2, sort_keys=False\n132:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:120-141`\n133:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_save -v`\n134: \n135: - [x] **T4.10**: Test save_metadata excludes None values\n136:   - Purpose: Verify model_dump(exclude_none=True) behavior\n137:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:143-156`\n138:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_save_excludes_none -v`\n139: \n140: - [ ] **T4.11**: Test update_metadata partial field update\n141:   - Purpose: Verify update_metadata applies partial updates correctly\n142:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py`\n143:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_update -v`\n144: \n145: - [ ] **T4.12**: Test update_metadata returns updated AgentMetadata\n146:   - Purpose: Verify update_metadata returns new AgentMetadata instance\n147:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py`\n148:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_se